overview: Our main character Serkan is a vlogger. While he was doing a YouTube video where he was answering fan questions, a fan named Halit asked strange questions, daring Serkan to go to a house that was haunted by a jinn. Serkan, with his girlfriend by his side accept the challenge and head to the haunted house.
tagline: They learned this spell from Harut and Marut through demons...
title: Azubel
